Presentation
------------
The Phopshore project is a tiny 3D graphics engine distributed under LGPL 
license. You can load 3D objetcs from files (for the moment, only PLY
format is supported) and translate, rotate, scale them independently.


Compiling
---------
This project is written in Java language. It's strongly recommended to use 
a compiler version >= 1.5. Then, you can compile the project by typing 
"make && java Main" in a terminal.
